If you want use `event_title`  in module field you can do this:

```{% if dynamic_page_hubdb_row %}     
  {% module "some_module" path='/path/to/module', label="some module", name_of_the_field='{{dynamic_page_hubdb_row.event_title}}' %}  
{% endif %}```
Just remember to change _name_of_the_field_ to the name of module field you want to use.
